parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated on the dashboard
the passenger airbag on/off light is not working properly
the airbag light will not turn off
and the airbag may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various issues, including faulty lighting, malfunctioning accessories, and even stalling or failure to start the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Headlights
taillights
and brake lights not functioning or malfunctioning
dashboard lights flickering
alarm system malfunctioning
and issues with the keyless entry system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to failure to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag light staying on
airbag failure to deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the door to lock or unlock unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents or trapping of occupants.
symptoms: Door locks not functioning
door unlocking unexpectedly
door locking while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starting system can cause the vehicle to fail to start, which can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle not starting
clicking sound when trying to start
battery draining.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause stalling, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine stalling
loss of power
difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door locks can cause the driver or passengers to be trapped in the vehicle, making it difficult or impossible to exit in an emergency situation, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The door locks do not respond to the key fob or manual unlocking
the door locks and unlocks randomly
the door locks but cannot be opened from the inside or outside
the door unlocks but then relocks when the handle is pulled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hood release can cause the hood to fly open while the vehicle is in motion, obstructing the driver's view and potentially causing an accident.
symptoms: The hood releases and flies open while the vehicle is in motion
the hood does not release when the latch is pulled
the hood latch is faulty or broken.
